  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "Prepare the vine leaves by rinsing and removing the stems",
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat and saute the onion and garlic until softened",
    "Add the rice, tomato paste, pomegranate molasses, spices, salt, and pepper to the pan and stir well",
    "Stuff each vine leaf with the rice mixture and roll into a neat package",
    "Place the dolmas in a large baking dish, seam side down, and cover with water",
    "Roast the dolmas in the preheated oven for 30 minutes",
    "Remove the dolmas from the oven and let them cool before serving"
